Hello,
 
I migrated from phpExcel 1.7.2 to 1.7.7 and the new addExternalSheet method seems buggy (even in trunk, 1.7.6, 1.7.5, 1.7.4, 1.7.3abc) : the external sheet loses merges on cells (styles are ok).
 
My code :
$reader = new PHPExcel_Reader_Excel5();
$excel = $reader->load($filename);
$allSheets = $excel->getAllSheets();
foreach ($excel->getAllSheets() as $sheet) {   
      $workbook->addExternalSheet($sheet);   
} 
$objWriter = PHPExcel_IOFactory::createWriter($workbook, 'Excel5');
$objWriter->save("/path");  
 
NB : the external file is generated by another (and old) library phpwrite_excel but it works fine with phpExcel 1.7.2
